    "text": "Ending Critical Race Theory in D.C. Public Schools Act\n\nThis bill prohibits any employee of the District of Columbia Public Schools or the District of Columbia Public Charter Schools from compelling a teacher or student to adopt, affirm, adhere to, or profess ideas that promote race or sex stereotyping or scapegoating."
